snippet.title: Next9World Global Journey
snippet.description: Next9World provides News, updates and Videos on Issues, Topics and Incidents from entertainment industry ranging from Bollywood, Hollywood and small screen. Our contents are originally created in English language. We also cover news updates and incidents of special significance from other categories concerning the latest lifestyles of modern generation.
